data.description: Welcome to this delightful home in Mableton, GA, strategically situated for fun and relaxation—just a stone's throw from Six Flags, Sweetwater Creek State Park, and 25 minutes from the Braves Stadium. With a roof only three years old, this property combines durability with style. The interior boasts a seamless flow from the cozy living spaces to the efficient kitchen, and outdoors, a fenced backyard with a patio awaits your summer evenings. Upstairs, find tranquil bedrooms ready to become your serene escape. This home is an ideal balance of comfort and convenience, perfect for making lasting memories.
